            It does not say that it is obliged to. Perhaps an amendment could have been tabled to delete that without actually going to the length of wishing to
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_28gc' title='Col. 28GC &mdash; HL Deb 07 June 2004 vol 662 c28GC' name='column_28gc' href='#column_28gc' rel='bookmark'>28GC</a>
